Class TransactionDTO

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.externalbank.otherbank.domain.dto.TransactionDTO
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.io.Serializable
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    OperationDTO, ScheduledOperationDTO
    public class TransactionDTO
extends java.lang.Object
implements java.io.Serializable
    This class follows the Data Transfer Object design pattern. It is a client view of a Transaction. This class only transfers data from a distant service to a client.
    Author:
    Isabelle Deligniere
